org.jasig.cas.authentication

Class DefaultAuthenticationResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jasig.cas.authentication.DefaultAuthenticationResult
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, AuthenticationResult

    public final class DefaultAuthenticationResult
extends java.lang.Object
implements AuthenticationResult
    The DefaultAuthenticationResult represents a concrete implementation of AuthenticationResult. It acts as a carrier for the finalized primary authentications established during processing of authentication events (posiblly multi-transactional) by CAS' authentication subsystem.
    Since:
    4.2
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
